# Theme Customization Guidelines

## SCSS Structure
- Main stylesheet: [assets/css/main.scss](mdc:assets/css/main.scss)
- Custom SCSS files in [_sass/](mdc:_sass/) directory
- Theme files in [_sass/minimal-mistakes/](mdc:_sass/minimal-mistakes/)

## Customization Approach
- Override theme variables in custom SCSS files
- Use [_sass/minimal-mistakes/_variables.scss](mdc:_sass/minimal-mistakes/_variables.scss) as reference
- Add custom styles to supplement theme, not replace
- Maintain responsive design principles

## Theme Configuration
- Skin set to "default" in [_config.yml](mdc:_config.yml)
- Available skins: air, aqua, contrast, dark, dirt, neon, mint, plum, sunrise
- Change `minimal_mistakes_skin` in config to switch themes

## Layout Customization
- Override layouts by creating files in [_layouts/](mdc:_layouts/)
- Customize includes by creating files in [_includes/](mdc:_includes/)
- Maintain compatibility with theme updates